creator: Thomas Moore
description:
LibriVox recording of Love Thee by Thomas Moore.
Read in English by Bruce Kachuk; David Lawrence; Newgatenovelist; Garth Burton; Greg Giordano; Ian King; Lee Ann Howlett; Leonard Wilson; Maria Kasper
This is the Weekly Poem for the week of November 29th, 2015. Another romantic love poem by the irish poet Thomas Moore. - Summary by Stav Nisser.
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
